\theta^{\prime}=\theta,\quad\frac{\sin\theta}{\sin\theta^{\prime\prime}}=\frac{\sqrt{\mu_{2}\varepsilon_{2}}}{\sqrt{\mu_{1}\varepsilon_{1}}^{\prime\prime}}=\frac{v_{1}}{v_{2}}=\frac{n_{2}}{n_{1}}
\]

